{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "峨嵋金顶大混战继续。萧秋水与李沉舟谈论丹药真假，李沉舟承认若不知丹药为假也会争夺。武当名宿铁骑道长与银瓶真人登临金顶，为柳随风杀害掌门太禅及守阙之事问罪李沉舟。银瓶一眼看出萧秋水功力与武艺不调。李沉舟揭露所谓《忘情天书》不过是神秘信件散布的假消息，真正闹出十几条人命的是无极仙丹。铁骑银瓶坚持血债血偿，李沉舟召出权力帮两大护法东一剑蓝放晴与西一剑白丹书。蓝放晴白丹书藏身巨钟内偷袭铁骑银瓶，四人激战后均负重伤追击而去。萧秋水与李沉舟展开辩论，质问权力帮不择手段的行事之道。少林代任掌门木叶大师与师弟豹象登场，木叶决意与李沉舟一战。木叶讲述自己从练剑、御剑、心明活杀剑法、慧剑到无剑的剑术历程，施展无剑手即剑令李沉舟倒飞，但李沉舟反击击倒暗中偷袭的豹象大师。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你争我夺，到头来便是这样的结果。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "若果你不知这些丹药是假的，是不是也投身于争夺之中？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "我吃了三颗\"无极先丹\"，一颗是给邵流泪逼服的，还有两颗，是宋姑娘顾全我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "这些药明珠都有跟师容说起，师容转告了我……她也服了一粒，一粒留给了我。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "她还说你是个真君子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "呔！权力帮的小子！快滚下来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "赫！你们何不自己爬上来！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "祖师爷饶命。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_ping",
      "speaker_name": "银瓶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "谁是李沉舟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈拜见两位前辈。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qi",
      "speaker_name": "铁骑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "小子，你也来了，姑娘呢？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_ping",
      "speaker_name": "银瓶",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "唉呀，怎么还是内功好，武功不济呀！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qi",
      "speaker_name": "铁骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里有没有李沉舟在？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qi",
      "speaker_name": "铁骑",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "很好，很好，",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_ping",
      "speaker_name": "银瓶",
      "listener": "char_tie_qi",
      "text": "英雄出少年，这句活真是没错，看来我们早该退休啦。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qi",
      "speaker_name": "铁骑",
      "listener": "char_yin_ping",
      "text": "不过还得办完此事才走。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_ping",
      "speaker_name": "银瓶",
      "listener": "char_tie_qi",
      "text": "这事儿不好办吧？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qi",
      "speaker_name": "铁骑",
      "listener": "char_yin_ping",
      "text": "就算办好，也要觅个好徒儿，单靠观里的庸才，怎能继承你我的衣钵？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_tie_qi",
      "text": "两位找我，有什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qi",
      "speaker_name": "铁骑",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "你有无一个手下，叫做柳随风？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qi",
      "speaker_name": "铁骑",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "那就是了。他在浣花萧家，杀了我派掌门太禅以及总观主持守阙；我要替我的徒孙们雪这个耻，报这个仇。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_ping",
      "speaker_name": "银瓶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "少林听说也丧了掌门天正。还有七大高手中排第四的木蝉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_ping",
      "speaker_name": "银瓶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "以及排第七的龙虎，据悉武功排第三的木叶和排第六的地极两人，也要前来金顶找柳五报仇雪恨……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qi",
      "speaker_name": "铁骑",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "又听说你在此地夺得《忘情天书》，你武功应已不错，加上《忘情天书》，那怎可以！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_tie_qi",
      "text": "是谁告诉你们我在这里拿到忘情天书的？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_ping",
      "speaker_name": "银瓶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "一封信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_yin_ping",
      "text": "一封信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qi",
      "speaker_name": "铁骑",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "是一封信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们之所以得知我在这里，还有《忘情天书》的事，都是因为收到一封信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为了一封神秘的信，我们莫名其妙的在峨嵋金顶，大杀一番……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "那未以前战狮古下巴被杀的传闻，又是怎么一回事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "古下巴那一行人，确是柳五和刀王等所杀的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以，也因此暴露了行踪。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_ping",
      "speaker_name": "银瓶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "那未说，这里并没有《忘情天书》这一回事了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_yin_ping",
      "text": "《忘情大书》却没有，无极仙丹却是先闹了十几条人命。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_ping",
      "speaker_name": "银瓶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "不管有没有，我们还是武当派的人，武当那一宗血案，还是要血债血偿的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_tie_qi",
      "text": "武林中以牙还牙，以血还血，本就是常事……两位剑，掌，功力三大绝，在下早如雷贯耳，但两位也知下知道。在我帮内，本有四大护法……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_ping",
      "speaker_name": "银瓶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "九手神鹰孙金猿和翻天蚊沈潜龙早已死了……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_yin_ping",
      "text": "还有蓝放晴，白丹书二人……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "东一剑，西一剑！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qi",
      "speaker_name": "铁骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别逃——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_ping",
      "speaker_name": "银瓶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追一一一",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "不公平。这不公平！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "怎样不公平？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "这就是你的部下，偷袭铁骑。银瓶，算什么英雄好汉！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "东一剑，西一剑与铁骑，银瓶武功相仿，但稍逊半筹，这我是知道的，他们同时也是宿敌，白丹书，蓝放晴二人要杀两个老道，那绝对是力有未逮的，难道我硬要规定他们面对面一对一的交手吗？那岂不是置这二个替权力之过不少汗马功劳的人于死地？如果是你的兄弟朋友，你又忍心这么做吗？所以我既不鼓励，也不阻止；我不出手，已经是很好的了。如果是你的弟兄，眼看要死了，妨不论他们出手得光明不光明，但你能忍得住不插手吗？嗯？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "其实要作为一个武林高手，首先要耳听八方，眼观六路，而且随时防患于未然，更常先置自己于绝地……铁骑，银瓶，武功虽高，但未免太天真，还不适合干这险诈江湖。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "我不知道你说得对不对，但贵帮之所以腐败，子弟之所以声名极恶，也就是为了这个，随时可以为目的而不择手段，甚至改变了原则来迁就手段，并不惜弃信背义。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一门一派，是非曲直，岂有如此简单？闻少林一脉，门户森严，门规更是天下闻名，但也出了木蝉。木蝶这等卖友求荣的人……",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "木叶、豹象两位大师，可以为然？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ye",
      "speaker_name": "木叶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "阿弥陀佛，人谁无恶，惟佛是善。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这次峨嵋金顶，真是热闹，冲着我李沉舟的面子，竟来了这么多前辈高人。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道我最喜欢用的是什么武器？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我不相信武器。我只相信我的拳头。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拳就是权。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "握拳就是握权。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出拳有力就是权力！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小人物不可一日无钱，惟大丈夫不可一日无权！所以我只相信我的拳头！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_mu_ye",
      "text": "少林寺对天正被杀之事，一直耿耿于怀，最主要是因为贵派方丈，武功可说已臻超凡入圣之境界，若不是死于暗算，是不可能败北的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ye",
      "speaker_name": "木叶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "善哉。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_mu_ye",
      "text": "少林数百年来名震天下，独树一格，向未见什么门派能把少林的实力消灭，这次天正既亡，但仍有木叶大师在，确是少林之福。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ye",
      "speaker_name": "木叶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "施主过奖。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_mu_ye",
      "text": "大师未出家时，是著名的心明活杀派的才子，剑术已到了能卸剑，驳剑、心剑合一的地步，而且也是一代暗器名家，满天星雨洒长街这几位暗器前辈，都曾在大师手下吃过大亏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ye",
      "speaker_name": "木叶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "可惜后来遇上唐老太太，没一个照面就败下阵来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_mu_ye",
      "text": "唐老太太绝足江湖，武功神秘莫测，大师能在她手下活命，己实属难得。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_mu_ye",
      "text": "所以在下要与大师过招交乎，定必要非常小心，非常的小心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ye",
      "speaker_name": "木叶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "李帮主尽管出手无妨，贫僧能不开杀戒、就尽可不造杀孽。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_mu_ye",
      "text": "谢了…",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ye",
      "speaker_name": "木叶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "今日我不找你，帮主也定找上少林，所以请恕贫僧放肆。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ye",
      "speaker_name": "木叶",
      "listener": "char_bao_xiang",
      "text": "阿弥陀佛。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "豹象",
      "listener": "char_mu_ye",
      "text": "方丈保重。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ye",
      "speaker_name": "木叶",
      "listener": "char_bao_xiang",
      "text": "如果不测，主持之职，还要师弟劳心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "豹象",
      "listener": "char_mu_ye",
      "text": "师兄不可说这不吉利的话。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ye",
      "speaker_name": "木叶",
      "listener": "char_bao_xiang",
      "text": "无所谓吉或不吉，我有剑，乃慧剑，剑斩一切妄幻。少林基业，尚要师弟垂顾。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "豹象",
      "listener": "char_mu_ye",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_mu_ye",
      "text": "大师，你的慧剑呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ye",
      "speaker_name": "木叶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "这剑是一流的剑，是从一位武林朋友处借来杀你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ye",
      "speaker_name": "木叶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "我以前练剑，后来能御剑，御剑时已鲜逢敌手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "李沉舟",
      "listener": "char_mu_ye",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ye",
      "speaker_name": "木叶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "未出家前，我己练得驳剑之术，创心明活杀剑法，当时可谓剑术之翘楚，而当之无愧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ye",
      "speaker_name": "木叶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "但我剑木的真正开始，乃在少林。在少林我练得慧剑，慧剑乃斩一切牵绊。即剑就是佛。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ye",
      "speaker_name": "木叶",
      "listener": "char_li_chen_zhou",
      "text": "后来我再得天正方丈大师兄的指点，又突破了慧剑的阶段。成了无剑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    }
  ],
